-- Air France-KLM votes against Alitalia's new business plan: source
-- 
-- Wed Nov 13, 2013 5:02pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/11/13/us-alitalia-airfrance-idUSBRE9AC17T20131113

 

 ROME  (Reuters) - Top shareholder Air France-KLM ( AIRF.PA ) has voted against Alitalia's revised business plan meant to make the cash-strapped Italian airline more profitable, a source close to the situation said on Wednesday. 
 Air France-KLM declined to comment. (Reporting by  Alberto Sisto  in Rome and Cyril Altmeyer in Paris; writing by  Agnieszka Flak ; editing by  Paola Arosio )